# 🚀 Social Media Content Assistant: Final Walkthrough

The project has been fully upgraded into a **production-ready Social Media Content Assistant**. This tool is designed for high performance, security, and a premium user experience.

---

## 🛠️ Advanced Modular Architecture

The backend has been refactored into specialized services to ensure scalability and ease of maintenance.

```mermaid
graph TD
    UI[React App] -->|POST /api/content/generate| Route[contentRoute.js]
    Route -->|Builds Prompt| PB[promptBuilder.js]
    Route -->|Calls API| OS[openaiService.js]
    OS -->|Retry Logic| OpenAI[OpenAI API]
    Route -->|Validation Layer| JSON[Strict JSON Validator]
    JSON -->|Clean Response| UI
```

### Key Backend Components:
- **[promptBuilder.js](file:///d:/my-gpt-blog-app/backend/services/promptBuilder.js)**: Orchestrates complex instructions for Instagram emojis, LinkedIn professionalism, and Twitter thread limits.
- **[openaiService.js](file:///d:/my-gpt-blog-app/backend/services/openaiService.js)**: Features a **Retry Mechanism** (1 retry) and input sanitization (max 500 chars).
- **[contentRoute.js](file:///d:/my-gpt-blog-app/backend/routes/contentRoute.js)**: Enforces a strict validation layer to ensure the AI always returns valid JSON (`hook`, `content`, `hashtags`, `engagementScore`).

